➜苏坛：《妆台》
http://www.sohu.com/a/438679285_100115135	50919
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201216/456254eda10647b38a9bb3a0ee885666.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《妆台》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当窗理云鬓，对镜贴花黄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张敞画眉，自有一段风流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妆台前总是有一位佳人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过还有朱颜辞境</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>岁月不会老</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沧桑年华会打磨一切</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我会一如既往地爱你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你终身未变的灵魂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>会让我在失忆中想起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然我不能执子之手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但我会目送你远去的背影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伫立于一棵枫树下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着落叶飘零</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201216/37a3a061dc7b4dcba33252c0fe3cc8e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
