➜河南诗人王琦伟：五绝·奇景（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/438694589_100115135	57235
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201216/53072cc802c647838114e8bb68bb1856.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·奇景（中华新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腾起日一轮，人间洒满金。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巨龙迎日舞，祥瑞照乾坤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.15</strong></p>
