<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·夜景（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冬夜冷无风，白河似镜平。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水天难悟辨，物像色光同。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
