➜内蒙古诗人孙虎：【双调.快活年】留守（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/438694991_100115135	57492
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201216/43a12040152d45588fef60a9a871346b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>【双调.快活年】留守（通韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/孙虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 回眸顷刻又一年，思君难入眠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生活所迫远家园，时刻心怀念。祈盼平安返，魂梦牵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201216/02e57424b67343f681f3afa3eb8a97f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>【中吕.十二月带尧民歌】锦瑟别谈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/孙虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云翻浪滚，落叶纷纷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相别太久，咫尺无音。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯万岑，尚可追寻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开又春，不见淑君。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
